text: Igor Wandtke (born 3 November 1990) is a German judoka. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the men's 73 kg event, in which he was eliminated in the third round by Sagi Muki. ==References== == External links == * * * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:German male judoka Category:Olympic judoka of Germany Category:Judoka at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Lübeck
